data.description: Step into this newly renovated 3-bedroom, 1.5-bathroom brick ranch residence, embracing a generous 2444 square feet of meticulously finished living space. The enduring charm and resilience of the classic brick exterior set the tone for this welcoming home.  Upon entry, discover a thoughtfully designed semi-open concept layout seamlessly merging the living, dining, and kitchen areas. Beyond providing an expansive and airy atmosphere, this design fosters interaction and connectivity, ideal for family gatherings and entertaining guests.  The interior has undergone tasteful updates, showcasing modern fixtures, a fresh coat of paint, and exquisite finishes. The kitchen stands out with its sleek countertops, new appliances, island, two countertop bar seating spaces, pantry, and ample cabinet space to cater to your culinary needs. The three bedrooms offer comfortable retreats, and the 1.5 bathrooms have been elegantly updated for your convenience.  Outside, the property unfolds with a spacious yard, offering endless possibilities for outdoor activities or gardening. Whether sipping morning coffee on the front porch or hosting a barbecue in the backyard, this property provides abundant space for your outdoor aspirations.  Take a firsthand look and seize the opportunity to make this your NEW Kentucky home!
